nodes.text: Ohlos was a human male officer of the Custom House of Cantonica on the spaceport of Canto Bight. After Kedpin Shoklop arrived to the planet Cantonica, where his prize was a two week all expenses paid vacation to Canto Bight, Ohlos stopped Kedpin with encountered problems, the first of which that he did not have a sponsorship chip. Then he and another officer, Lorala, decided to let him go due to the work required had he remained detained.
